{"type":"message","id":"1fc68f74","parentId":"d16de4d0","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:12:42.607Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09c2c7891525c9bd0169cbc8433a108194b0bfddbdf7a673d1\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_kzsolkEMB3SrxPTwA6zkbLHo|fc_09c2c7891525c9bd0169cbc84c9fac8194a3ba27886173628a","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:/Users/User-OEM/Desktop/content-factory/auto_content_factory/docs/contracts/s1/s1_scene_director_contract.md","oldText":"### Structural / traceability fields\nEach scene should also contain:\n- `start_word`\n- `end_word`\n- `estimated_scene_word_count`\n","newText":"### Structural / traceability fields\nEach scene should also contain:\n- `start_word`\n- `end_word`\n- `estimated_scene_word_count`\n\n### Span coordinate rule\nFor `scene_director` outputs, `start_word` and `end_word` should be **relative to the batch**, not absolute to the full script.\n\nThis means:\n- each batch defines its own local word coordinate system\n- the first word in the batch is word `1`\n- downstream deterministic logic may later convert or enrich spans with global coordinates if needed\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:/Users/User-OEM/Desktop/content-factory/auto_content_factory/docs/contracts/s1/s1_scene_director_contract.md\",\"oldText\":\"### Structural / traceability fields\\nEach scene should also contain:\\n- `start_word`\\n- `end_word`\\n- `estimated_scene_word_count`\\n\",\"newText\":\"### Structural / traceability fields\\nEach scene should also contain:\\n- `start_word`\\n- `end_word`\\n- `estimated_scene_word_count`\\n\\n### Span coordinate rule\\nFor `scene_director` outputs, `start_word` and `end_word` should be **relative to the batch**, not absolute to the full script.\\n\\nThis means:\\n- each batch defines its own local word coordinate system\\n- the first word in the batch is word `1`\\n- downstream deterministic logic may later convert or enrich spans with global coordinates if needed\\n\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ytK9CCssImCvIWURayWGi2Np|fc_09c2c7891525c9bd0169cbc84c9fc081949356a9094aae02a4","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:/Users/User-OEM/Desktop/content-factory/auto_content_factory/docs/contracts/s1/s1_scene_director_output_validator_contract.md","oldText":"### Minimum expected input\n- run/job context sufficient for logging/reference\n- `batch_id`\n- source batch text\n- source batch range metadata\n- `scene_director` batch output path or loaded object\n- required field specification / contract assumptions\n","newText":"### Minimum expected input\n- run/job context sufficient for logging/reference\n- `batch_id`\n- source batch text\n- source batch range metadata\n- `scene_director` batch output path or loaded object\n- required field specification / contract assumptions\n\n### Coordinate rule\nThe validator should treat scene `start_word` / `end_word` values as **batch-relative coordinates**.\n\nThis means validation should happen in the local coordinate system of the batch, not against absolute script-global word indices.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:/Users/User-OEM/Desktop/content-factory/auto_content_factory/docs/contracts/s1/s1_scene_director_output_validator_contract.md\",\"oldText\":\"### Minimum expected input\\n- run/job context sufficient for logging/reference\\n- `batch_id`\\n- source batch text\\n- source batch range metadata\\n- `scene_director` batch output path or loaded object\\n- required field specification / contract assumptions\\n\",\"newText\":\"### Minimum expected input\\n- run/job context sufficient for logging/reference\\n- `batch_id`\\n- source batch text\\n- source batch range metadata\\n- `scene_director` batch output path or loaded object\\n- required field specification / contract assumptions\\n\\n### Coordinate rule\\nThe validator should treat scene `start_word` / `end_word` values as **batch-relative coordinates**.\\n\\nThis means validation should happen in the local coordinate system of the batch, not against absolute script-global word indices.\\n\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_03jUm4tTTH9fp3TPuaRGWFDS|fc_09c2c7891525c9bd0169cbc84c9fc8819480ff942daca5eea9","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:/Users/User-OEM/Desktop/content-factory/auto_content_factory/docs/contracts/s1/s1_scene_director_output_validator_contract.md","oldText":"- scene word spans are ordered and non-overlapping\n- scene coverage accounts for the intended batch source span\n","newText":"- scene word spans are ordered and non-overlapping\n- scene coverage accounts for the intended batch source span in batch-relative coordinates\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:/Users/User-OEM/Desktop/content-factory/auto_content_factory/docs/contracts/s1/s1_scene_director_output_validator_contract.md\",\"oldText\":\"- scene word spans are ordered and non-overlapping\\n- scene coverage accounts for the intended batch source span\\n\",\"newText\":\"- scene word spans are ordered and non-overlapping\\n- scene coverage accounts for the intended batch source span in batch-relative coordinates\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":205,"output":522,"cacheRead":78976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79703,"cost":{"input":0.0005125,"output":0.00783,"cacheRead":0.019743999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0280865}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774962748725,"responseId":"resp_09c2c7891525c9bd0169cbc83f8f90819493c9aa9f4958df29"}}
