 off listing carrier deck into the sea. Chaotic, visceral war photography grain.\",\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\01_pre_production\\agents\\scene_director\\EXAMPLES.md:39:      \"duration_estimate\": \"18s\"\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\01_pre_production\\agents\\scene_director\\EXAMPLES.md:44:      \"visual_direction\": \"Burning Japanese carrier listing heavily to starboard, survivors abandoning ship into oil-slicked water, distant smoke columns marking the graves of the other three carriers on the horizon, fading afternoon light. Somber, final documentary tone.\",\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\01_pre_production\\agents\\scene_director\\EXAMPLES.md:46:      \"duration_estimate\": \"7s\"\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\01_pre_production\\agents\\scene_director\\EXAMPLES.md:57:- Cada visual_direction tem 20+ palavras com detalhes espec�ficos de �poca, c�mara e atmosfera\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\01_pre_production\\agents\\scene_director\\EXAMPLES.md:81:      \"visual_direction\": \"Renaissance papal chamber bathed in warm candlelight, Pope Alexander VI seated on ornate throne examining a golden chalice, Caravaggio-style chiaroscuro lighting with deep shadows, rich crimson robes against dark stone walls, small vial of white powder barely visible on the table beside papal documents.\",\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\01_pre_production\\agents\\scene_director\\EXAMPLES.md:83:      \"duration_estimate\": \"15s\"\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\01_pre_production\\agents\\scene_director\\EXAMPLES.md:88:      \"visual_direction\": \"Opulent banquet hall lit by hundreds of candles, Cesare Borgia watching guests with a predatory smile from the head of a long table laden with food and wine, unsuspecting nobles raising goblets in toast, Rembrandt-style warm golden tones with menacing shadows in the background. Renaissance oil painting aesthetic.\",\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\01_pre_production\\agents\\scene_director\\EXAMPLES.md:90:      \"duration_estimate\": \"15s\"\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\01_pre_production\\agents\\scene_director\\EXAMPLES.md:95:      \"visual_direction\": \"Dark vineyard terrace at dusk, Pope Alexander clutching his throat at a candlelit outdoor table, overturned wine goblet spilling dark liquid across white linen, Cesare reaching for his father in horror, harsh torchlight casting dramatic shadows across agonized faces. Titian-style composition.\",\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\01_pre_production\\agents\\scene_director\\EXAMPLES.md:97:      \"duration_estimate\": \"16s\"\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\01_pre_production\\agents\\scene_director\\EXAMPLES.md:102:      \"visual_direction\": \"Gaunt Cesare Borgia alone in a vast empty throne room, slumped in chair with hollow eyes, abandoned papal regalia scattered on the floor, single shaft of cold morning light cutting through darkness, dust motes in the air suggesting decay and abandonment. Metaphorical collapse of dynasty.\",\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\01_pre_production\\agents\\scene_director\\EXAMPLES.md:104:      \"duration_estimate\": \"14s\"\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror