{"type":"message","id":"a5c244f7","parentId":"8a357e49","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:46:44.634Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_t1W0NYGUzAbWOvAkcuLFsjPq|fc_09c2c7891525c9bd0169cbd045154081948dbce271dbadbae1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\implementation\\00_IMPLEMENTATION_LOG.md:47:| scene_director_runner.py | Python + gpt-4.1-mini + API key | Agente OpenClaw + GPT-5.4 mini + OAuth | ALTA |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\implementation\\s1\\01_prototype_v1.md:28:scene_director_runner.py  [PROTOTYPE - Python directo, gpt-4.1-mini, API key]\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\implementation\\s1\\01_prototype_v1.md:77:| `scene_director_runner.py` | Agente OpenClaw, GPT-5.4 mini, OAuth | Python directo, gpt-4.1-mini, API key | Modelo errado + pay-per-use |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\runtime\\s1\\s1_start.py:12:from runtime.s1.scene_director_runner import run_scene_director, save_screenplay\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\runtime\\s1\\s1_start.py:60:        screenplay = run_scene_director(script_raw, job, config, model=model)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\runtime\\s1\\s1_start.py:64:    screenplay_path = save_screenplay(screenplay, video_root)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\runtime\\s1\\s1_start.py:81:                screenplay = run_scene_director(script_raw, job, config, model=model)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\runtime\\s1\\s1_start.py:82:                save_screenplay(screenplay, video_root)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\runtime\\s1\\scene_director_runner.py:20:def run_scene_director(\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\co