{"type":"message","id":"2e30e284","parentId":"f6749ea8","timestamp":"2026-03-31T16:49:28.352Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6KTc004m2stO2dg5ti5dVNIV|fc_09c2c7891525c9bd0169cbfb147c008194aed2168a3f8362f6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# WORKFLOW.md — SM-S1\n\n## Canonical sector flow\n1. Run `s1_preflight_checker`\n2. Run `s1_paths_resolver`\n3. Plan script batches via `script_batch_planner`\n4. Build scene_director payloads via `scene_director_io_adapter`\n5. Schedule scene_director batches with controlled parallelism\n6. Merge scene_director outputs via `screenplay_merger`\n7. Validate screenplay\n8. If validation fails, use `retry_planner`\n9. Plan polish batches via `tts_polish_batch_planner`\n10. Build tts_polish payloads via `tts_polish_io_adapter`\n11. Schedule tts_polish batches with controlled parallelism\n12. Merge polish outputs via `tts_polish_merger`\n13. Validate polish\n14. If validation fails, use `retry_planner`\n15. Build `scene_bible.json`\n16. Validate scene bible schema\n17. Write/check checkpoints\n18. Summarize sector result via `s1_result_summarizer`\n19. Complete or fail the sector\n\n## Important workflow rules\n- Preserve persisted file contracts\n- Preserve original narration separately from TTS-polished narration\n- Use selective retry when possible\n- Do not overwrite original screenplay with polished narration\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774975768237}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f8b5a95","parentId":"2e30e284","timestamp":"2026-03-31T16:49:28.474Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_wyFiGkiJ8V4ka0LFkn0IgV21|fc_09c2c7891525c9bd0169cbfb147c848194b85a801ab6edd25d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# OPERATORS.md — SM-S1\n\n## scene_director\n\n### Role\nTransformar batches do script bruto em cenas estruturadas para `screenplay.json`.\n\n### Receives\n- batch payload prepared by `scene_director_io_adapter`\n- `scene_words_range`\n- batch text\n- output path contract\n\n### Returns\nBatch result containing scene objects with at least:\n- `scene_id`\n- `narration_original`\n- `visual_direction`\n- `mood`\n- `duration_estimate`\n\n### Does not do\n- TTS polish\n- scene bible building\n- sector-level retry logic\n\n---\n\n## tts_polish\n\n### Role\nTransformar batches pequenos de cenas em narração polida para TTS sem alterar significado.\n\n### Receives\n- polish batch payload prepared by `tts_polish_io_adapter`\n- original scene narration\n- `tts_polish_rules`\n- output path contract\n\n### Returns\nBatch result containing, at minimum:\n- `scene_id`\n- `narration_original`\n- `narration_tts`\n- optional `changes`\n\n### Does not do\n- overwrite original screenplay\n- sector-level retry logic\n- scene bible building\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774975768352}}
